data.description: Custom built log home with 95 acres. This home has everything you could ever want in a home, in a retreat, whatever you’re looking for. Walk into a beautiful great room and sit by the hand-laid stone fireplace and custom built spiral log staircase. Open floorplan into your kitchen and dining for all your entertaining. Also downstairs is your own master suite with walk-in closet and whirlpool bathtub. Upstairs is another 3 bedrooms. Walk through the great room and into your family room for more entertaining. Keep going and you’ll come into your very own indoor basketball court and gaming area with an axe throwing wall and then into a huge indoor pool! You’ll never have to vacation way from your home! Down in the basement is gaming space, bar, built-in bunks for more sleeping, movie room and a gym space. Outside is beautiful landscaping, firepits, horseshoe pit, fully stocked pond all overlooked by the treks deck. Property has hunting blinds, food plots and even a motocross track, attached heated 2 stall garage and detached 2 stall garage for more storage of equipment, toys, etc. This home comes fully furnished along with a Kubota tractor. Square footage was measured by Sellers agent
